              "text": "DC 31 Fortitude",
              "type": "stat_block_section"
            }
          ],
          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "A creature entering or beginning its turn in a furnerico's fetid aura must succeed at a DC 31 Fortitude or be sickened 1; the creature also becomes enfeebled 1 until the end of their next turn. A creature that succeeds at its save is temporarily immune to all furnerico fetid auras for 1 minute.",
