          "name": "Hydrophobic",
          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "A furnerico avoids water and won't willingly approach within five feet of a body of water. It won't initiate an attack against any creature that's soaking wet with water or that has the water trait. A furnerico takes a \u20132 circumstance penalty to its attack rolls against such creatures who attack it.",
